    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously kept in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been treated with a multi-year ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it has never been smoked in. Every switch, button, and digital display functions as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service history binder documenting every fluid change and inspection. Recently fitted with a fresh set of high-performance tires and having just undergone a preventative multi-point inspection, this car requires absolutely nothing but a new enthusiast owner. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 43900.0,
